\c 1
\p
\v 1 From the church leader. Hoseya indodana kabeyeri ensukwini zaboUziya loJothamu loAhazi loHezekhiya, amakhosi akoJuda, lensukwini zikaJerobowamu indodana kaJowasi inkosi yakoIsrayeli.
\v 2 Lapho iN\sc KOSI\sc* iqalisa ukukhuluma ngoHoseya yathi kuye: Hamba uyethatha umfazi oliwule, uzale abantwana bokuwulwa; ngoba ilizwe leli liyawula kakhulu ngokudela iN\sc KOSI\sc*.
\v 3 UHoseya wasehamba wathatha uGomeri indodakazi kaDibilayimi; wakhulelwa, wamzalela indodana.
\v 4 IN\sc KOSI\sc* yasisithi kuye: Ithe ibizo layo \add uthi\add* yiJizereyeli, ngoba kuseseyisikhatshana ngizaphindisela igazi leJizereyeli phezu kwendlu kaJehu, ngiwuqede umbuso wakoIsrayeli.
\p
\v 5 Ngalolosuku ngizakwephula idandili likaIsrayeli esigodini seJizereyeli.
\p
\v 6 UGomeri wabuya wakhulelwa, wazala indodakazi. Yathi kuHoseya: Ithe ibizo uthi nguLoruhama, ngoba kangisayikuyihawukela indlu kaIsrayeli ukuze ngibathethelele.
\p
\v 7 Kodwa ngizahawukela indlu yakoJuda, ngibakhulule ngeN\sc KOSI\sc* uNkulunkulu wabo; njalo kangiyikubakhulula ngedandili, loba ngenkemba, loba ngempi, ngamabhiza, kumbe ngabagadi bamabhiza.
\p
\v 8 Esekhunyuliwe ebeleni uLoRuhama, wabuya wakhulelw
